# Wrangler local dev / `opennextjs-cloudflare preview` (not used by plain `next dev`).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored). One KEY=value per line.
#
# Use for Worker-only secrets. `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` for the browser must be present at
# `next build` time (see `.env.*.example`), not only here.

# EXAMPLE_SECRET_KEY=replace-me
